This is the best golf game I‚Äôve ever played on iOS. The gold standard. Download it already.

The only con really is trying to collect all the skins, hats, & trails. This is where the money making part of the game is, so I can‚Äôt fault them that much. Just wish card packs wouldn‚Äôt give so many duplicates of things.

All in all, amazing game. You‚Äôll have plenty of fun with it. I recommend buying the package to remove ads so you can truly get the full experience.
